Privacy Policy – DahabChain Wallet

Effective Date: September 13, 2025

DahabChain Wallet (“we”, “our”, or “the App”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and share information when you use our mobile wallet app designed for Somali users. By using DahabChain Wallet, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information from you when you use DahabChain Wallet:

Personal Information: Phone number (+252), email address, full name.

Account Information: Transaction history, wallet balance, reward points, payment methods.

Device Information: Device type, operating system, IP address, app usage data, location data (if enabled).

Customer Support Data: Messages, inquiries, and support interactions.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

To authenticate and verify your account.

To process deposits, withdrawals, and transfers.

To manage your account and provide customer support.

To improve our services and app functionality.

To send updates, notifications, or marketing (if you consent).

For analytics and fraud prevention.

3. Information Storage and Security

We take the security of your data seriously:

All personal information is stored securely using industry-standard encryption.

Sensitive data such as authentication credentials are encrypted and protected.

We use trusted third-party services like Firebase Storage for secure data storage.

Access to personal data is restricted to authorized personnel only.

4. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access your personal information.

Correct or update inaccurate information.

Request deletion of your account and personal data.

Export your data in a standard format.

To exercise your rights, please contact us at the details below.

5. Sharing of Information

We do not sell your personal information. Your information may be shared:

With trusted service providers to enable app functionality.

For legal compliance or to protect the safety of users.

In anonymized form for analytics and app improvement.

6. Cookies and Tracking

The App may use cookies or similar technologies for:

Analyzing app usage and performance.

Improving user experience.

Marketing and promotional purposes (with user consent).

7. Children’s Privacy

DahabChain Wallet is not intended for children under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us:

Email: dahabchainwallet@gmail.com

Address: DahabChain Wallet Headquarters, Somalia

By using DahabChain Wallet, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
